divs: Sighting DetailsOne of the condos by my home has a web cam on the roof. every morning I like to look at the night shot (picture not video)the camara took of the beach the night before. Lately its bean getting a few shots I cant understand, I dont think this many planes would be in the same area at the same time. I have a ton of these pictures. and some are the same time each night. Not saying they are U.F.Os, just dont know what they could be. I also live about 17-20 miles from palm beach international airport. I would love to find out what it is, even if its nothing. thanks for your time.
